00:00:13.162 --> 00:00:16.301
What are you about to make?
Rajma Veg Curry (Kidney Beans Curry)

00:00:27.226 --> 00:00:30.018
Ingredients required to make Rajma Veg Curry

00:00:30.557 --> 00:00:46.838
Kidney Beans, Cashews, Coconut, Green Chillies, Tomatoes, Onions, Chopped Vegetables,
 Coriander, Cumin, Cloves, Cinnamon, Turmeric, Salt, Chilli Powder, Oil

00:00:54.211 --> 00:00:58.537
Take a pan and heat it up

00:01:04.682 --> 00:01:15.679
Boil some chopped potatoes, carrots, beans, green peas,
capsicum, bottlegourd &amp; cucumber

00:01:26.856 --> 00:01:30.911
Half them half boiled with a little salt

00:01:43.278 --> 00:01:52.095
Soak the kidney beans in water overnight
and then boil them

00:02:04.335 --> 00:02:08.425
Heat some oil in the pan

00:02:16.388 --> 00:02:20.016
Add 1/2 tsp cumin

00:02:21.392 --> 00:02:27.169
Add some crushed cloves and cinnamon

00:02:41.886 --> 00:02:47.242
Add some chopped onions, tomatoes &amp; green chillies

00:03:11.825 --> 00:03:15.957
Close the lid and cook for 2 mins

00:03:28.596 --> 00:03:32.322
Add a little turmeric

00:03:34.288 --> 00:03:39.085
Add salt as required

00:03:41.478 --> 00:03:45.475
Add some red chilli powder (as per taste)

00:03:49.773 --> 00:03:54.009
Add a cup of the soaked &amp; boiled kidney beans

00:04:03.422 --> 00:04:10.183
Grind some cashews and fresh
 coconut to make a fine paste

00:04:12.840 --> 00:04:17.116
Add a cup of this paste

00:04:31.542 --> 00:04:34.040
Add a little water

00:04:39.362 --> 00:04:45.860
Add the half boiled vegetables

00:04:58.706 --> 00:05:02.168
Close the lid and cook for 2-5 mins

00:05:14.524 --> 00:05:18.567
Add some coriander

00:05:22.270 --> 00:05:26.294
Turn off the stove and take the curry into a serving bowl

00:05:30.997 --> 00:05:34.157
Garnish with some cashews and some coriander

